# Keep these rules but adapt as needed:
# - Never commit: .env, secrets, API keys, passwords
# - Never commit: node_modules (regenerate with npm install)
# - Never commit: __pycache__, .pytest_cache
# - Safe to commit: requirements.txt, package.json, .env.example, source code
